msgstr "使用"

#: .\kikai_tools.json
msgid "Magnetic field generator (suit)"
msgid_plural "Magnetic field generator (suit)s"
msgstr[0] "磁场发生器（套装）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Magnetic field generator (suit)'}
#: .\kikai_tools.json
msgid ""
"You can manipulate the surrounding metal and create a machine. It consumes "
"enormous power."
msgstr "你可以操控周围的金属并制造机器。它消耗巨大的能量。"

#: .\martialarts.json
msgid "Eskrima"
msgstr "埃斯克rima"

#: .\martialarts.json
msgid "Fencing"
msgstr "击剑术"

#: .\martialarts.json
msgid "Krav Maga"
msgstr "以色列格斗术"

#: .\martialarts.json
msgid "Medieval Swordsmanship"
msgstr "中世纪剑术"

#: .\martialarts.json
msgid "Ninjutsu"
msgstr "忍术"

#: .\martialarts.json
msgid "Niten Ichi-Ryu"
msgstr "二天一流"

#: .\martialarts.json
msgid "Silat"
msgstr "席拉特"

#: .\martialarts.json
msgid "Fior Di Battaglia"
msgstr "战斗之花"

#: .\mizu_item.json
msgid "Snorkelling"
msgid_plural "Snorkellings"
msgstr[0] "浮潜"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Snorkelling'}
#: .\mizu_item.json
msgid ""
"It is a tool to let you breathe even underwater. However, you will feel "
"stuffy while you are not used to it."
msgstr "这是一种让你即使在水下也能呼吸的工具。然而，在你习惯之前会感到闷热。"

#: .\mizu_item.json
msgid "Simple snorkel"
msgid_plural "Simple snorkels"
msgstr[0] "简易呼吸管"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Simple snorkel'}
#: .\mizu_item.json
msgid ""
"A snorkel made of duct tape and rubber hose is coming. It seems that my "
"breath will suck."
msgstr "一个由管道胶带和橡胶软管制成的呼吸管即将到来。看来我的呼吸会很费力。"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "vorpal weapons"
msgstr "斩首武器"

#. ~ Description for vorpal weapons
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"A collection of assorted gear, weapons, recipes and more. Machine translated"
" from Japanese."
msgstr "一系列各式装备、武器、配方等。由日语机器翻译而来。"

#: .\vo_ammo_types.json
msgid "Blood transfusion pack"
msgstr "输血包"

#: .\vo_ammo_types.json
msgid "Blood for transfusion"
msgid_plural "Blood for transfusion"
msgstr[0] "输血用血液"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Blood for transfusion', 'str_pl': 'Blood for
#. transfusion'}
#: .\vo_ammo_types.json
msgid "It is cleaned blood."
msgstr "这是经过清洁的血液。"

#: .\vo_ammo_types.json
msgid "Blood transfusion pack (off)"
msgid_plural "Blood transfusion pack (off)"
msgstr[0] "输血包（关闭）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Blood transfusion pack (off)', 'str_pl':
#. 'Blood transfusion pack (off)'}.
#: .\vo_ammo_types.json
msgid "I started blood transfusion."
msgstr "我开始输血了。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Blood transfusion pack (off)', 'str_pl': 'Blood
#. transfusion pack (off)'}
#: .\vo_ammo_types.json
msgid "It is a transfusion pack kept clean. It can be used as it is."
msgstr "这是一个保持清洁的输血包。可以直接使用。"

#: .\vo_ammo_types.json
msgid "Blood transfusion pack (on)"
msgid_plural "Blood transfusion pack (on)s"
msgstr[0] "输血包（开启）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Blood transfusion pack (on)'}.
#: .\vo_ammo_types.json
msgid "I stopped transfusing."
msgstr "我停止了输血。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Blood transfusion pack (on)'}
#: .\vo_ammo_types.json
msgid ""
"It is a transfusion pack kept clean. It is strange to see blood coming "
"inside of me."
msgstr "这是一个保持清洁的输血包。看到血液流入体内感觉很奇怪。"

#: .\vo_ammo_types.json
msgid "Blood transfusion pack (empty)"
msgid_plural "Blood transfusion pack (empty)"
msgstr[0] "输血包（空）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Blood transfusion pack (empty)', 'str_pl':
#. 'Blood transfusion pack (empty)'}
#: .\vo_ammo_types.json
msgid ""
"It is an empty transfusion pack. It can be reused if it washes cleanly. "
"Probably it will be okay."
msgstr "这是一个空的输血包。如果清洗干净可以重复使用。大概没问题吧。"

#: .\vo_armor.json
msgid "Smoke-proof mask(XL)"
msgid_plural "Smoke-proof mask(XL)s"
msgstr[0] "防烟面具（XL）"

#: .\vo_armor.json
msgid "Arm Warmer(XL)"
msgid_plural "Arm Warmer(XL)"
msgstr[0] "护臂（XL）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Arm Warmer(XL)', 'str_pl': 'Arm Warmer(XL)'}
#: .\vo_armor.json
msgid "Large, soft, snug cloth sleeves to keep your exotic anatomy warm."
msgstr "宽大、柔软、贴合的布袖，为您奇特的解剖结构保暖。"

#: .\vo_armor.json
msgid "A quiver (leg)"
msgid_plural "A quiver (leg)s"
msgstr[0] "箭袋（腿部）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'A quiver (leg)'}
#: .\vo_armor.json
msgid ""
"It is a small quiver hanging from the waist. The drooping quiver interferes "
"with one leg. You can put in 10 pieces."
msgstr "这是一个挂在腰间的箭袋。垂下的箭袋会妨碍一条腿。可以放入10支箭。"

#: .\vo_armor.json
msgid "Power assist suit (off)"
msgid_plural "Power assist suit (off)s"
msgstr[0] "助力服（关闭）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Power assist suit (off)'}.
#: .\vo_armor.json
msgid "I turned on the assist function."
msgstr "我开启了辅助功能。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Power assist suit (off)'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Power Assist Suit (On)'}
#: .\vo_armor.json
msgid ""
"It is an auxiliary tool that makes it easy to lift heavy objects. It's not "
"for battle, so it's not durable."
msgstr "这是一种辅助工具，便于举起重物。它不是为战斗设计的，因此不耐用。"

#: .\vo_armor.json
msgid "Power Assist Suit (On)"
msgid_plural "Power Assist Suit (On)s"
msgstr[0] "助力服（开启）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Power Assist Suit (On)'}.
#: .\vo_armor.json
msgid "Assist function turned off."
msgstr "辅助功能已关闭。"

#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "survivor belt"
msgid_plural "survivor belts"
msgstr[0] "幸存者腰带"

#. ~ Use action holster_msg for {'str': 'survivor belt'}.
#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "You sheath your %s"
msgstr "你将你的%s收鞘。"

#. ~ Use action holster_prompt for {'str': 'survivor belt'}.
#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "Sheath blade"
msgstr "鞘刃"

#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "noise emitter (on)"
msgid_plural "noise emitter (on)s"
msgstr[0] "噪音发射器（开启）"

#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "quarterstaff"
msgid_plural "quarterstaffs"
msgstr[0] "长棍"

#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "ironshod quarterstaff"
msgid_plural "ironshod quarterstaffs"
msgstr[0] "铁头长棍"

#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "powered quarterstaff"
msgid_plural "powered quarterstaffs"
msgstr[0] "动力长棍"

#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "headgear"
msgid_plural "headgears"
msgstr[0] "头饰"

#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "lobotomizer"
msgid_plural "lobotomizers"
msgstr[0] "脑叶切除器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'lobotomizer'}
#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid ""
"This is a hand-forged collapsible tool that has two axe heads and sharp "
"shovel-like tip on one end.  It can be used as a shovel, or you could chop "
"some zombies with it instead."
msgstr "这是一把手工锻造的可折叠工具，一端有两个斧头和一个锋利的铲状尖端。它可以用作铲子，或者你也可以用它来砍杀一些僵尸。"

#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "dive knife"
msgid_plural "dive knives"
msgstr[0] "潜水刀"

#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "halberd"
msgid_plural "halberds"
msgstr[0] "戟"

#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "naginata"
msgid_plural "naginatas"
msgstr[0] "薙刀"

#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "glaive"
msgid_plural "glaives"
msgstr[0] "斩矛"

#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "battle axe"
msgid_plural "battle axes"
msgstr[0] "战斧"

#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "broadsword"
msgid_plural "broadswords"
msgstr[0] "阔剑"

#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "flammenschwert (aus)"
msgid_plural "flammenschwerter (aus)"
msgstr[0] "火焰剑（熄灭）"

#. ~ Use action lacks_fuel_message for {'str': 'flammenschwert (aus)',
#. 'str_pl': 'flammenschwerter (aus)'}.
#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "Dein Flammenschwert hat keinen Brennstoff mehr."
msgstr "你的火焰剑燃料已耗尽。"

#. ~ Use action success_message for {'str': 'flammenschwert (aus)', 'str_pl':
#. 'flammenschwerter (aus)'}.
#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "Die Klinge deines Schwertes brennt!"
msgstr "你的剑刃燃烧起来了！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flammenschwert (aus)', 'str_pl':
#. 'flammenschwerter (aus)'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flammenschwert', 'str_pl': 'flammenschwerter'}
#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid ""
"Ein großes zweihändiges Schwert aus Deutschland, an dessen Klinge sich, "
"unter Zuführung von Benzin, eine anhaltende Flamme erzeugen lässt.  Es ist "
"eine sehr mächtige Waffe."
msgstr "一把来自德国的巨大双手剑，通过添加汽油，可以在剑刃上产生持续的火焰。这是一件非常强大的武器。"

#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "flammenschwert"
msgid_plural "flammenschwerter"
msgstr[0] "火焰剑"

#. ~ Use action charges_extinguish_message for {'str': 'flammenschwert',
#. 'str_pl': 'flammenschwerter'}.
#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "Deinem Flammenschwert ist der Brennstoff ausgegangen!"
msgstr "你的火焰剑燃料用完了！"

#. ~ Use action noise_message for {'str': 'flammenschwert', 'str_pl':
#. 'flammenschwerter'}.
#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "Das Feuer um deine Schwertklinge leuchtet hell!"
msgstr "你剑刃周围的火焰明亮地燃烧着！"

#. ~ Use action voluntary_extinguish_message for {'str': 'flammenschwert',
#. 'str_pl': 'flammenschwerter'}.
#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "Die Flamme deines Schwertes erlischt."
msgstr "你剑上的火焰熄灭了。"

#. ~ Use action water_extinguish_message for {'str': 'flammenschwert',
#. 'str_pl': 'flammenschwerter'}.
#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "Dein Schwert zischt und erlischt."
msgstr "你的剑发出嘶嘶声并熄灭了。"

#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "shishkebab (off)"
msgid_plural "shishkebabs (off)"
msgstr[0] "烤肉串剑（关闭）"

#. ~ Use action failure_message for {'str': 'shishkebab (off)', 'str_pl':
#. 'shishkebabs (off)'}.
#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "Aw, dangit.  It fails to start!"
msgstr "啊，糟糕。它启动失败了！"

#. ~ Use action lacks_fuel_message for {'str': 'shishkebab (off)', 'str_pl':
#. 'shishkebabs (off)'}.
#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "This thing needs some fuel!"
msgstr "这东西需要一些燃料！"

#. ~ Use action success_message for {'str': 'shishkebab (off)', 'str_pl':
#. 'shishkebabs (off)'}.
#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "Let's dance, Zeds!"
msgstr "来跳舞吧，僵尸们！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'shishkebab (off)', 'str_pl': 'shishkebabs
#. (off)'}
#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid ""
"This is a large blade with a fuel pipe on the side, and a small tank and "
"igniter built into the insulated hilt.  When filled with gasoline, the blade"
" can be made scorching hot to singe enemies and light your way.  Use to "
"ignite."
msgstr "这是一把大型刀刃，侧面有燃料管，绝缘刀柄内建有小油箱和点火器。当注入汽油时，刀刃可以变得灼热，以灼伤敌人并照亮你的道路。使用以点燃。"

#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "shishkebab (on)"
msgid_plural "shishkebabs (on)"
msgstr[0] "烤肉串剑（开启）"

#. ~ Use action auto_extinguish_message for {'str': 'shishkebab (on)',
#. 'str_pl': 'shishkebabs (on)'}.
#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "Bummer, man!  Your shishkebab's flame flickers and dies out."
msgstr "真倒霉，伙计！你的烤肉串剑火焰闪烁并熄灭了。"

#. ~ Use action charges_extinguish_message for {'str': 'shishkebab (on)',
#. 'str_pl': 'shishkebabs (on)'}.
#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "Uncool, outta gas!  Your shishkebab's flame goes out."
msgstr "不妙，没油了！你的烤肉串剑火焰熄灭了。"

#. ~ Use action noise_message for {'str': 'shishkebab (on)', 'str_pl':
#. 'shishkebabs (on)'}.
#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "Your shishkebab crackles!"
msgstr "你的烤肉串剑噼啪作响！"

#. ~ Use action voluntary_extinguish_message for {'str': 'shishkebab (on)',
#. 'str_pl': 'shishkebabs (on)'}.
#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "Peace out.  Your shishkebab's flame dies."
msgstr "熄火了。你的烤肉串剑火焰熄灭了。"

#. ~ Use action water_extinguish_message for {'str': 'shishkebab (on)',
#. 'str_pl': 'shishkebabs (on)'}.
#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "Your shishkebab hisses in the water and goes out."
msgstr "你的烤肉串剑在水中嘶嘶作响并熄灭了。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'shishkebab (on)', 'str_pl': 'shishkebabs (on)'}
#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid ""
"This is a large blade with a fuel pipe on the side, and a small tank and "
"igniter built into the insulated hilt.  The blade is glowing brightly.  Use "
"to shut off the gas."
msgstr "这是一把大型刀刃，侧面有燃料管，绝缘刀柄内建有小油箱和点火器。刀刃正明亮地发光。使用以关闭燃气。"

#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "katana"
msgid_plural "katanas"
msgstr[0] "武士刀"

#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "torch (lit)"
msgid_plural "torches (lit)"
msgstr[0] "火炬（点燃）"

#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "tiger claws"
msgid_plural "tiger claws"
msgstr[0] "虎爪"

#: .\vo_kaihen.json .\vo_weapons.json
msgid "bionic claws"
msgid_plural "bionic claws"
msgstr[0] "仿生爪"

#: .\vo_kaihen.json .\vo_weapons.json
msgid "monomolecular blade"
msgid_plural "monomolecular blades"
msgstr[0] "单分子刀片"

#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "tinfoil hat"
msgid_plural "tinfoil hats"
msgstr[0] "锡箔帽"

#: .\vo_kaihen.json
msgid "pair of rollerskates"
msgid_plural "pairs of rollerskates"
msgstr[0] "一双轮滑鞋"

#: .\vo_ranged.json
msgid "Rifle (stone / pneumatic assault rifle)"
msgid_plural "Rifle (stone / pneumatic assault rifle)s"
msgstr[0] "步枪（石制/气动突击步枪）"

#: .\vo_ranged.json
msgid ""
"Large pneumatic rifle with spiral stones. Although not quiet, the killing "
"power is extremely high."
msgstr "大型气动步枪，配备螺旋石弹。虽不安静，但杀伤力极高。"

#: .\vo_ranged.json
msgid "semi-auto"
msgstr "半自动"

#: .\vo_ranged.json
msgid "auto"
msgstr "自动"

#: .\vo_shield.json
msgid "Ballistic shield (large)"
msgid_plural "Ballistic shield (large)"
msgstr[0] "防弹盾牌（大型）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Ballistic shield (large)', 'str_pl': 'Ballistic
#. shield (large)'}
#: .\vo_shield.json
msgid ""
"It is a big shield made by Kevlar. It has size enough to cover the whole "
"body and high bulletproof performance, and it is adopted for security "
"maintenance organization of each country."
msgstr "这是一种由凯夫拉制成的大型盾牌。尺寸足以覆盖全身，防弹性能高，被各国安保维护组织采用。"

#: .\vo_shield.json
msgid "Ballistic shield (middle)"
msgid_plural "Ballistic shield (middle)"
msgstr[0] "防弹盾牌（中型）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Ballistic shield (middle)', 'str_pl': 'Ballistic
#. shield (middle)'}
#: .\vo_shield.json
msgid ""
"It is a Kevlar shield. It is compatible with portability and minimal "
"protection range, and it is mainly used in special forces."
msgstr "这是一种凯夫拉盾牌。兼顾便携性和最小防护范围，主要用于特种部队。"

#: .\vo_shield.json
msgid "Riot Shield"
msgid_plural "Riot Shield"
msgstr[0] "防暴盾牌"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Riot Shield', 'str_pl': 'Riot Shield'}
#: .\vo_shield.json
msgid ""
"It is a transparent shield made of reinforced resin. It is light in weight "
"for size, has wide protection range and high visibility."
msgstr "这是一种由增强树脂制成的透明盾牌。重量轻，防护范围广，可见度高。"

#: .\vo_shield.json
msgid "Pot shield"
msgid_plural "Pot shield"
msgstr[0] "锅盖盾牌"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Pot shield', 'str_pl': 'Pot shield'}
#: .\vo_shield.json
msgid ""
"It is a lid of a pan. I cloth is wrapped around the handle so as not to "
"damage my hands. If you look only at the form you will not be able to insist"
" as a shield."
msgstr "这是一个平底锅的盖子。手柄上缠有布料以防伤手。仅看外形，你很难坚持说它是盾牌。"

#: .\vo_shield.json
msgid "Bulletproof briefcase"
msgid_plural "Bulletproof briefcase"
msgstr[0] "防弹公文包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bulletproof briefcase', 'str_pl': 'Bulletproof
#. briefcase'}
#: .\vo_shield.json
msgid ""
"Kevlar board is embedded inside this briefcase. The loading capacity is "
"reduced by that much, but we will protect our lives as well as our luggage."
msgstr "这个公文包内嵌有凯夫拉板。装载容量因此减少，但它能保护你的生命和行李。"

#: .\vo_tools.json
msgid "Toy bomb"
msgid_plural "Toy bombs"
msgstr[0] "玩具炸弹"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Toy bomb'}.
#: .\vo_tools.json
msgid "I started a bomb."
msgstr "我启动了炸弹。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Toy bomb'}
#: .\vo_tools.json
msgid "Sprinkle homemade white sticky matter."
msgstr "洒出自制的白色粘稠物质。"

#: .\vo_tools.json
msgid "Trouble bomb (start)"
msgid_plural "Trouble bomb (start)s"
msgstr[0] "麻烦炸弹（启动）"

#. ~ Use action no_deactivate_msg for {'str': 'Trouble bomb (start)'}.
#: .\vo_tools.json
msgid "You've already armed the %s, try throwing it instead."
msgstr "你已经启动了%s，试着把它扔出去吧。"

#. ~ Use action sound_msg for {'str': 'Trouble bomb (start)'}.
#: .\vo_tools.json
msgid "*Pucchu*."
msgstr "*噗嗤*。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Trouble bomb (start)'}
#: .\vo_tools.json
msgid ""
"Sprinkle homemade white sticky matter. Please throw it before you get "
"caught!"
msgstr "洒出自制的白色粘稠物质。在被抓住前请把它扔出去！"

#: .\vo_tools.json
msgid "Telescopic mop"
msgid_plural "Telescopic mops"
msgstr[0] "伸缩拖把"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Telescopic mop'}
#: .\vo_tools.json
msgid ""
"It is a telescopic mop. Performance does not change even if it is less than "
"half the size of conventional products."
msgstr "这是一种伸缩拖把。即使尺寸不到传统产品的一半，性能也不变。"

#: .\vo_tools.json
msgid "Autologous blood transfusion kit (off)"
msgid_plural "Autologous blood transfusion kit (off)s"
msgstr[0] "自体输血套件（关闭）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Autologous blood transfusion kit (off)'}.
#: .\vo_tools.json
msgid "I connected the blood collector to my body."
msgstr "我将采血器连接到了身体上。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Autologous blood transfusion kit (off)'}
#: .\vo_tools.json
msgid ""
"It is a kit for using blood for transfusion. Save it when you are healthy, "
"and use it when you need it. Start turning blood on by turning it on."
msgstr "这是一个用于输血的套件。健康时保存血液，需要时使用。通过开启来启动输血。"

#: .\vo_tools.json
msgid "Autologous blood transfusion kit (on)"
msgid_plural "Autologous blood transfusion kit (on)s"
msgstr[0] "自体输血套件（开启）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Autologous blood transfusion kit (on)'}.
#: .\vo_tools.json
msgid "I pulled out the blood collector."
msgstr "我取出了采血器。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Autologous blood transfusion kit (on)'}
#: .\vo_tools.json
msgid ""
"It is a kit for using blood for transfusion. Blood is being accumulated ... "
"· · ·. Saved blood can be used as it is, or it can be removed from "
"production. Let's draw it out when it is full."
msgstr "这是一个用于输血的采血套件。血液正在积累中……· · ·。储存的血液可以直接使用，也可以从生产中移除。等它满了再抽取吧。"

#: .\vo_tools.json
msgid "Brain washing device (off)"
msgid_plural "Brain washing device (off)s"
msgstr[0] "洗脑装置（关闭）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Brain washing device (off)'}.
#: .\vo_tools.json
msgid "I have a headache···."
msgstr "我头痛欲裂···。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Brain washing device (off)'}
#: .\vo_tools.json
msgid ""
"It is an electromagnetic wave weapon which acts on the opponent's brain "
"using sunlight. Because of its nature, it can only be used while hitting the"
" sun and once turned on it can not be turned off as long as the sun is out. "
"You can defend by winding aluminum foil on the head."
msgstr ""
"这是一种利用阳光作用于对手大脑的电磁波武器。由于其特性，它只能在阳光照射时使用，并且一旦开启，只要太阳还在，就无法关闭。可以通过在头上缠绕铝箔来防御。"

#: .\vo_tools.json
msgid "Brain washing device (on）"
msgid_plural "Brain washing device (on）s"
msgstr[0] "洗脑装置（开启）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Brain washing device (on）'}
#: .\vo_tools.json
msgid ""
"It is an electromagnetic wave weapon which acts on the opponent's brain "
"using sunlight. Because of its nature, it can only be used while hitting the"
" sun and once turned on it can not be turned off as long as the sun is out. "
"Why is it also effective for machines?"
msgstr ""
"这是一种利用阳光作用于对手大脑的电磁波武器。由于其特性，它只能在阳光照射时使用，并且一旦开启，只要太阳还在，就无法关闭。为什么它对机器也有效？"

#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid "Objective turret (stop)"
msgid_plural "Objective turret (stop)s"
msgstr[0] "目标炮塔（停止）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Objective turret (stop)'}
#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid ""
"Leadworks LLC's T-107A1 Interdictor, an automated .50BMG antimateriel rifle."
"  Credited with forestalling countless car-bombing attempts, it has always "
"been kept under extremely tight control, so as to itself maintain extremely "
"tight control of its area.  And then the Cataclysm struck."
msgstr ""
"Leadworks "
"LLC的T-107A1拦截者，一款自动化的.50BMG反器材步枪。它因阻止了无数汽车炸弹袭击而备受赞誉，一直受到极其严格的控制，以便对其区域保持极严密的控制。然后大灾变降临了。"

#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid "Search light (MIL standard) (stop)"
msgid_plural "Search light (MIL standard) (stop)s"
msgstr[0] "探照灯（军用标准）（停止）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Search light (MIL standard) (stop)'}
#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid ""
"Three high-powered searchlights with automated search AI and mounting, "
"continually seeking targets."
msgstr "三个高功率探照灯，配备自动搜索AI和安装座，持续寻找目标。"

#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid "Security robot (stop)"
msgid_plural "Security robot (stop)s"
msgstr[0] "安保机器人（停止）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Security robot (stop)'}
#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid ""
"The Northrop Watchman X-1 is a production series of heavily armored combat "
"robots.  Initially designed for military patrol and escort service, it rolls"
" on a set of hydraulic treads and is armed with a 9x19mm SMG."
msgstr ""
"诺斯罗普守望者X-1是一款重型装甲战斗机器人的生产系列。最初设计用于军事巡逻和护送服务，它依靠一组液压履带移动，并装备有一把9x19毫米冲锋枪。"

#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid "Cleaning robot (stop)"
msgid_plural "Cleaning robot (stop)s"
msgstr[0] "清洁机器人（停止）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cleaning robot (stop)'}
#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid ""
"The Ford Sanitron, a utility robot designed for cleaning up waste material "
"in hazardous conditions."
msgstr "福特清洁机器人，一种专为在危险环境下清理废弃物而设计的实用型机器人。"

#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid "Police Robot (Stop)"
msgid_plural "Police Robot (Stop)s"
msgstr[0] "警察机器人（停止）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Police Robot (Stop)'}
#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid ""
"One of the many models of armored law enforcement robots employed shortly "
"before the collapse of civilization.  Solar powered like many other robots, "
"it maintains its programmed pursuit of law and order, propelled on a trio of"
" omni wheels."
msgstr ""
"这是文明崩溃前不久部署的众多装甲执法机器人型号之一。像许多其他机器人一样，它由太阳能驱动，依靠三个全向轮推进，持续执行其程序化的法律与秩序追求。"

#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid "Mining robot (stop)"
msgid_plural "Mining robot (stop)s"
msgstr[0] "采矿机器人（停止）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Mining robot (stop)'}
#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid ""
"A snake-like, segmented robot built to tunnel into the ground and detonate "
"landmines."
msgstr "一种蛇形、分段的机器人，设计用于钻入地面并引爆地雷。"

#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid "Tripod type robot (stop)"
msgid_plural "Tripod type robot (stop)s"
msgstr[0] "三足型机器人（停止）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tripod type robot (stop)'}
#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid ""
"The Honda Regnal, a tall robot walking on three spidery legs.  For weapons, "
"it has a trio of spiked retractable cables and a flamethrower mounted on its"
" head."
msgstr "本田Regnal，一种高大的机器人，以三条蜘蛛般的腿行走。武器方面，它有三条带刺的可伸缩电缆和一个安装在头部的火焰喷射器。"

#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid "Chicken Walker (stop)"
msgid_plural "Chicken Walker (stop)s"
msgstr[0] "鸡足步行机（停止）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Chicken Walker (stop)'}
#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid ""
"The Northrup ATSV, a massive, heavily-armed and armored robot walking on a "
"pair of reverse-jointed legs.  Armed with a 40mm anti-vehicle grenade "
"launcher, 5.56 anti-personnel gun, and the ability to electrify itself "
"against attackers, it is an effective automated sentry, though production "
"was limited due to a legal dispute."
msgstr ""
"诺斯罗普 "
"ATSV，一台巨大的、全副武装的重型机器人，依靠一对反关节腿行走。它配备了一门40毫米反车辆榴弹发射器、一把5.56毫米反人员枪械，并能对攻击者进行电击，是一款高效的自动哨兵，尽管由于法律纠纷，其生产数量有限。"

#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid "Unmanned Tank (Stop)"
msgid_plural "Unmanned Tank (Stop)s"
msgstr[0] "无人坦克（停止）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Unmanned Tank (Stop)'}
#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid ""
"The Northrup Emancipator is the first and only automated tank ever produced,"
" made shortly after the split-up of Northrup Grumman.  Clad in depleted "
"uranium plating, and armed with advanced munitions and a 120-mm gun, it is "
"capable of delivering extraordinary firepower."
msgstr ""
"诺斯罗普解放者是第一款也是唯一一款生产的自动化坦克，在诺斯罗普·格鲁曼公司拆分后不久制造。它覆盖着贫铀装甲，配备先进弹药和一门120毫米火炮，能够提供非凡的火力。"

#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid "Explorer (stop)"
msgid_plural "Explorer (stop)s"
msgstr[0] "探索者（停止）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Explorer (stop)'}
#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid ""
"A small, round turret which extends from the floor.  Two SMG barrels swivel "
"360 degrees."
msgstr "一个从地板延伸出来的小型圆形炮塔。两把冲锋枪枪管可360度旋转。"

#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid "Monitoring robot (stop)"
msgid_plural "Monitoring robot (stop)s"
msgstr[0] "监控机器人（停止）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Monitoring robot (stop)'}
#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid ""
"A fusion-driven UAV largely comprised of a high-resolution camera lens, this"
" spheroid robot hovers above the ground, silent witness to the carnage and "
"mayhem around it."
msgstr "一种聚变驱动的无人机，主要由高分辨率摄像头镜头组成，这个球形机器人悬浮在地面上方，默默见证着周围的屠杀与混乱。"

#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid "Broken cyborg (stop)"
msgid_plural "Broken cyborg (stop)s"
msgstr[0] "损坏的赛博格（停止）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Broken cyborg (stop)'}
#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid ""
"A robot body with the head of a human.  All kinds of electronic wires and "
"devices are implanted in its head.  Patches of skin look diseased or "
"rotting.  This cyborg moves erratically and has a confused and deranged look"
" in its eyes."
msgstr ""
"一个机器人身体，长着人类的头颅。各种电子线路和设备植入其头部。皮肤斑块看起来像是病变或腐烂。这个赛博格行动怪异，眼中流露出困惑和疯狂的神色。"

#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid "Riot suppressing robot (stop)"
msgid_plural "Riot suppressing robot (stop)s"
msgstr[0] "防暴镇压机器人（停止）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Riot suppressing robot (stop)'}
#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid ""
"Nonviolent riot-control bot.  Designed to suppress riots and make mass "
"arrests of those participating.  Though its relaxation gas is by far its "
"best-known weapon, it carries a blinding flash and a low-powered stungun for"
" self-defense--in addition to its supply of electronic handcuffs."
msgstr ""
"非暴力防暴机器人。设计用于镇压骚乱并大规模逮捕参与者。尽管其松弛气体是其最著名的武器，但它还配备致盲闪光和低功率电击枪用于自卫——此外还有电子手铐供应。"

#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid "High speed robot (stop)"
msgid_plural "High speed robot (stop)s"
msgstr[0] "高速机器人（停止）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'High speed robot (stop)'}
#: .\vo_turret.json
msgid ""
"A insectoid robot the size of a small dog, designed for home security.  "
"Armed with two close-range tazers, it can skate across the ground with great"
" speed."
msgstr "一种小型犬大小的昆虫状机器人，专为家庭安防设计。配备两把近程电击枪，能以极快速度滑过地面。"

#: .\vo_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "training wheels"
msgstr "训练轮"

#: .\vo_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "A floating ring"
msgstr "一个漂浮的环"

#: .\vo_weapons.json
msgid "Boxing gloves with stone"
msgid_plural "Boxing gloves with stone"
msgstr[0] "嵌石拳击手套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Boxing gloves with stone', 'str_pl': 'Boxing
#. gloves with stone'}
#: .\vo_weapons.json
msgid ""
"It is a stuffed stone divided into two into a large ounce red boxing glove. "
"I only need to beat up on my strength, so I do not need any detailed work. "
"It is about 19.6 ounces."
msgstr "这是一块填充石料分割成两半制成的大型盎司红色拳击手套。我只需依靠力量击打，无需任何精细加工。重量约为19.6盎司。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bionic claws', 'str_pl': 'bionic claws'}
#: .\vo_weapons.json
msgid "Short and sharp claws made from a high-tech metal."
msgstr "由高科技金属制成的短而锋利的爪子。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'monomolecular blade'}
#: .\vo_weapons.json
msgid ""
"A foot-long blade made from high-tech alloy and edged with bonded "
"nanocrystals."
msgstr "一英尺长的高科技合金刀刃，边缘镶有结合纳米晶体。"

#: .\vo_weapons.json
msgid "Pata"
msgid_plural "Patas"
msgstr[0] "帕塔拳剑"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Pata'}
#: .\vo_weapons.json
msgid ""
"It is a long sword with a structure resembling Jamadahar, which is fitted "
"with swords in armor of a shape like a gauntlet covering the forearm, the "
"outside of the fist. Although it is a powerful weapon, you can not pick up "
"objects because the arms are fixed."
msgstr "这是一把结构类似贾马达尔的长剑，装配在形如覆盖前臂和拳背的臂甲中。虽是强力武器，但因手臂被固定而无法拾取物品。"

#: .\vo_weapons.json
msgid "Battle Hook"
msgid_plural "Battle Hooks"
msgstr[0] "战斗钩"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Battle Hook'}
#: .\vo_weapons.json
msgid ""
"It is a simple weapon just having a claw attached to the long handle. I can "
"only pull it down, but it may be tossed off as much as a rotten head."
msgstr "这只是一种在长柄上附加爪钩的简单武器。仅能向下拉扯，但可能像腐烂头颅般被甩脱。"

#: .\vo_weapons.json
msgid "Laser sword (off)"
msgid_plural "Laser sword (off)s"
msgstr[0] "激光剑（关闭）"

#. ~ Use action lacks_fuel_message for {'str': 'Laser sword (off)'}.
#: .\vo_weapons.json
msgid "It seems that energy is not enough."
msgstr "似乎能量不足。"

#. ~ Use action success_message for {'str': 'Laser sword (off)'}.
#: .\vo_weapons.json
msgid "I heard a low groaning sound."
msgstr "我听到低沉的呻吟声。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Laser sword (off)'}
#: .\vo_weapons.json
msgid ""
"It is my original lightsaber that is supposed to work with UPS. Although it "
"is possible to irradiate an illegal output laser and burn enemies, it is a "
"drawback that electric power is applied too much. It is also a substitute "
"for acetylene lamp."
msgstr "这是我原创的光剑，本应与UPS配合使用。虽能发射非法输出激光灼伤敌人，但耗电过大是缺点。也可替代乙炔灯。"

#: .\vo_weapons.json
msgid "Laser sword (on)"
msgid_plural "Laser sword (on)s"
msgstr[0] "激光剑（开启）"

#. ~ Use action charges_extinguish_message for {'str': 'Laser sword (on)'}.
#: .\vo_weapons.json
msgid "The energy expired."
msgstr "能量已耗尽。"

#. ~ Use action noise_message for {'str': 'Laser sword (on)'}.
#: .\vo_weapons.json
msgid "voooom... voooom..."
msgstr "嗡……嗡……"

#. ~ Use action voluntary_extinguish_message for {'str': 'Laser sword (on)'}.
#: .\vo_weapons.json
msgid "The light blade disappeared."
msgstr "光刃消失了。"

#. ~ Use action water_extinguish_message for {'str': 'Laser sword (on)'}.
#: .\vo_weapons.json
msgid "It seems he had forgotten waterproofing."
msgstr "他似乎忘了做防水处理。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Laser sword (on)'}
#: .\vo_weapons.json
msgid ""
"It is my original lightsaber that is supposed to work with UPS. Although it "
"is possible to irradiate an illegal output laser and burn enemies, it is a "
"drawback that electric power is applied too much. Since there is no "
"substance, attacks can not be handled."
msgstr "这是我原创的光剑，本应与UPS配合使用。虽能发射非法输出激光灼伤敌人，但耗电过大是缺点。由于没有实体，无法格挡攻击。"

#: .\vo_weapons.json
msgid "Sword of plutonium"
msgid_plural "Sword of plutoniums"
msgstr[0] "钚之剑"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sword of plutonium'}
#: .\vo_weapons.json
msgid "It is a beautiful sword that fires lightly."
msgstr "这是一把微微发光的美丽长剑。"
